think it was that funny.

18
00:01:03,647 --> 00:01:07,277
It's taken me many years
to actually get the film.

19
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:09,987
I mean, I liked it,
but then I liked it more.

20
00:01:10,070 --> 00:01:13,370
