on Joel and Ethan.

155
00:09:12,135 --> 00:09:15,264
I think they're recognizing it for what it is.
It's a brilliant film.

156
00:09:15,347 --> 00:09:19,853
And that's why our society is in crisis.
'Cause of The Big Lebowski.

157
00:09:20,268 --> 00:09:22,896
You don't need the marijuana
to watch the movie, kids.

158
00:09:22,979 --> 00:09:25,073
It's good without it.

159
00:09:25,148 --> 00:09:27,492
<i>TURTURRO: The Dude.
What kind of example is he?</i>

160
00:09:27,567 --> 00:09:29,240
The Dude abides.

161
00:09:29,319 --> 00:09:32,072
It goes on forever.
This stuff could never end.

162
00:09:32,155 --> 00:09:33,475
Who knows what happened
to Walter?

163
00:09:33,531 --> 00:09:35,611
He could have become a priest
or something like that.

164
00:09:35,867 --> 00:09:38,666
Maybe there'll be
a Lebowski Junior.

165
00:09:38,745 --> 00:09:40,497
'Cause he's 10 years old now.

166
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:44,380
I wonder where that dude is today, must
be about 10 years old now, you know.

167
00:09:44,459 --> 00:09:46,461
I wonder what he's doing.

168
00:09:46,670 --> 00:09:50,140
Probably selling pot to
all his friends. I don't know.

